rules.description_html:
&lt;!-- SC_OFF --&gt;&lt;div class="md"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Posts must include:
- Ages, genders and relationship length
- Include a TL;DR! - a brief summary at the end of your post. No &amp;quot;See title&amp;quot;.**
- Sufficient spelling, grammar and formatting to be readable&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- SC_ON --&gt;

&lt;!-- SC_OFF --&gt;&lt;div class="md"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Posts must be:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;First person, not for someone else&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Specific, clearly stated questions about your situation, not general, polling etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A desire for input, not just to vent&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- SC_ON --&gt;

&lt;!-- SC_OFF --&gt;&lt;div class="md"&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;No general questions, polling or ‘opinion gathering’.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;No meta complaints (about the sub). If you are unhappy here, reddit elsewhere.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;No questions directed at a single gender or group.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;No politics!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;No gift or activity questions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Updates -&amp;quot;UPDATE&amp;quot; needs to be in the title. Link to the previous post, which cannot be deleted or removed. Original post more than 48 hours old. One update only. &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- SC_ON --&gt;

&lt;!-- SC_OFF --&gt;&lt;div class="md"&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Do not feed the trolls. Use the report button&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;No abuse and victim blaming&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Do not use uncivil, negatively gendered, ableist, sexist or bigoted language.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Avoid tangential discussions,&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;No photos, links, or videos&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Do not post or request personal information&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Do not mention upvotes or downvotes. We do not allow vote manipulation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;No AI-Generated advice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Do not use the sub to push your personal agenda&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comments must contain constructive and helpful advice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- SC_ON --&gt;

&lt;!-- SC_OFF --&gt;&lt;div class="md"&gt;&lt;p&gt;We provide instant bans for:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advocating, suggesting or justifying violence. Even as a joke.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Crossposting content from here to another sub, including your own page&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Do not repost removed material unless specifically instructed to edit and repost&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Egregious bigotry and abusiveness&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Brigading&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- SC_ON --&gt;

&lt;!-- SC_OFF --&gt;&lt;div class="md"&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be respectful to posters and other commenters&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Focus on helping the OP&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use your experience to form advice but put yourself in the place of others as well&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Thank people for good advice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;If you are tempted to make an angry reply, use the report button instead&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- SC_ON --&gt;
